# bin/

Intent command-line tools and executable scripts for steel thread management, project configuration, and LLM integration. This directory contains the main CLI entry points and utilities for the Intent system.

## Files

- `intent` -- Main entry point; routes commands to subcommands and plugins
- `intent_helpers` -- Shared utility functions for version management and YAML-to-JSON conversion
- `intent_config` -- Configuration library; JSON parsing, project root detection, config loading
- `intent_bootstrap` -- Initial Intent setup for first-time users
- `intent_init` -- Create new Intent projects with directory structure and configuration
- `intent_doctor` -- Diagnose and fix configuration issues
- `intent_info` -- Display Intent installation and project status
- `intent_help` -- Display help for Intent commands
- `intent_st` -- Manage steel threads (create, list, edit, show)
- `intent_backlog` -- Wrapper for Backlog.md task management integration
- `intent_bl` -- Shorthand alias for backlog
- `intent_task` -- Manage Backlog tasks linked to steel threads
- `intent_status` -- Sync steel thread status with Backlog task completion
- `intent_migrate` -- Migrate embedded tasks from steel threads to Backlog.md
- `intent_upgrade` -- Upgrade STP projects to Intent v2.3.3
- `intent_llm` -- Manage LLM prompts and context files
- `intent_fileindex` -- Create and manage file indexes with checkbox states
- `intent_treeindex` -- Generate .treeindex directory summaries using Claude
- `intent_organise` -- Organize steel threads into status directories
- `intent_main` -- Backward compatibility wrapper (stp command alias)
- `intent_minimal` -- Minimal wrapper for Phase 1 testing
